#Retail Analytics Dashboard in Excel

##Project Overview
This project demonstrates the development of a retail sales analytics solution using an OLAP data model and an interactive dashboard in Microsoft Excel. 
The model integrates sales, products, stores, and customer data to support multidimensional business analysis.

##Tools
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- OLAP Data Model
- Dashboard Design
- Data Visualization

##Methods Applied
- Data modeling using related tables
- OLAP-based multidimensional analysis
- Sales aggregation and filtering
- Interactive dashboard development
- Geographic sales visualization
- Customer segmentation by gender
- Product category analysis

##Results
The project provides an interactive environment for analyzing sales performance, customer purchasing behavior, product categories, and store efficiency.
The dashboard allows users to filter data by year and product category, supporting business decision-making and performance evaluation.
